          <msContents>
            <summary>Livre de recettes contre les maladies des chevaux: with additional receipts by a later 17th cent. hand, etc. On the first leaf: 'Ce present livre est a moy leaunar richard' and below 'LE AV NAR'. The last section is headed in capital letters: 'Leszacament [sic] Quil F Avlt Ferre A Vn Companon Qant Il Se Vevlt Passer Maistre De Loffice De Marich Avt A Tovlouze 1608' This is in the form of Question and Answer. At the end 'Fin de leszaman [sic] de toulouze 1608 escrit par darnol estant a paris 1608'. On the first fly-leaf autograph of V. De Savary [19th cent.].</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="" source="IANA">French</textLang>
            <msItem n="1" xml:id="MS_229_1">
              <author/>
              <title type="original">Darnol</title>
              <title type="standard"/>
              <textLang mainLang="" source="IANA">French</textLang>
              <filiation/>
              <filiation/>
            </msItem>
          </msContents>
